data.description: Beautifully updated, 3 level home, located in the wonderful community of Northwood, ND.  Recent renovations include an open floor plan, large primary bedroom suite, kitchen and bathroom remodels, lighting upgrades, gorgeous original hardwood floors, and fully finished lower level. The exterior boasts your own private, park-like space, with mature landscaping. Large deck with pergola, playset, and 2 additional storage sheds.  Award winning K-12 school system.  A quick 25 minutes to GF AFB.  35 minutes to Grand Forks.
